ly identified the gerber baby some legends claim that the baby is sally gerber herself the reason why the company itself was established another urban legend says that richard nixon was the original gerber baby a huge draw to the image of the gerber baby is largely due to the fact that this baby is alone not in the presence of adults innocently peering straight into the eyes of the consumer this innocent outward gaze was surely a marketing if not psychological technique to suck in female motherconsumers this forced many mothers to seek the happiness of their own child via the eyes of the iconic gerber baby thus the notion that if their babies were fed gerber they would also be as content smiley and cute as the gerber baby tax break and expansionedit gerber products company specimen stock certificate c in september  gerbers fremont facilities were designated as a michigan agricultural renaissance zone receiving  million in tax breaks over  years in order to receive the incentives gerber agreed to continue its employment in fremont at  jobs and invest  million in its fremont facilities over the course of the next ten years however to get the full  years of tax breaks gerber agreed to increase employment by  and spend a total of  million on its facilities the tax breaks have been largely supported despite large revenue losses by local governments  in losses per year for the city of fremont  of their budget and  a year for newaygo county it is estimated local governments would give up potentially  million in revenue over the  years as part of the tax break both the county and the city will be working with the fremont area community foundation to receive funds in the initial years to help with specific projects and programs the fremont public school district would receive assistance through the state school aid formula nestlé nutrition north america ceo kurt schmidt said that the fremont research and development center will be one of  worldwide nestlé product technology centers and also include scientific research for baby and infant nutritional products it is expected that the new investment will help make newaygo county a global leader in scientific research gerber productsedit gerber turkey chicken and meat sticks in water gerber oatmeal gerbers boxed food gerber strained peas see alsoedit gerber singles referencesedit  bentley amy chapter  inventing baby food taste health and the industrialization of the american diet np np nd  print  novartis completes its business portfolio restructuring divesting gerber for usd  billion to nestlé novartis  april   novartis completes divestment program with transfer of gerber baby foods business archived january   at the wayback machine novartis  september   growing up gerber  questions with cmo aileen stocks brandchannel  april  retrieved  may    bentley amy chapter  inventing baby food taste health and the industrialization of the american diet np np nd  print  bentley amy chapter  inventing baby food taste health and the industrialization of the american diet np np nd  print  alexander dave september   tax breaks could save gerber  million extend company operations  years the muskegon chronicle retrieved    alexander dave december   gerber investment to create  jobs the muskegon chronicle retrieved    alexander dave september   gerber gets unanimous backing for lowtax zone the muskegon chronicle retrieved   external linksedit official website gerber life insurance official website v t e nestlé brands appliances babynes dolce gusto nescafé alegria nescafé barista nespresso specialt baby nutrition babynes cerelac gerber graduates mucilon naturnes nestum nidal brand bear brand nido ptit baking libbys pumpkin toll house bottled water arrowhead buxton contrex deer park hépar ice mountain ozarka acqua panna perrier poland spring pure life quézac san pellegrino vittel zephyrhills cereals cheerios chocapic chokella cini minis clusters cocoa crisp cookie crisp corn flakes country corn flakes curiou